CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,FThe Women's Rights Network in Northern
OL,8,FIreland (WRN NI) has launched legal
OL,9,Fproceedings against Feile an Phobail
OL,10,Fafter event organisers failed to
OL,11,Freinstate their cancelled event.
OL,13,FFeile an Phobail said they are
OL,14,F"extremely disappointed" with the
OL,15,Fdecision while the Women's Rights
OL,16,FNetwork said they felt they had "no
OL,17,Fchoice".
OL,19,FThe Communities Minister Gordons Lyons
OL,20,Falso weighed in on the controversy.
OL,26,@lD@HrrqD@VrruD@Brr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
