FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,FFeile an Phobail is Ireland's biggest
OL,8,Fcommunity arts festival, with more
OL,9,Fthan 600 events taking place across 50
OL,10,Fvenues in Belfast.
OL,12,FThe Women's Rights Network were
OL,13,Fscheduled to run an event called
OL,14,FRespects, Rights and Reality in August.
OL,16,FIt describes itself as a network of
OL,17,Fwomen who promote the human rights of
OL,18,Fwomen and girls.
OL,26,@lD@HrroD@Brr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,FHowever organisers of the west Belfast
OL,8,Ffestival cancelled the event earlier
OL,9,Fthis week.
OL,11,FIn an intial statement Feile said it
OL,12,F"was unaware from the initial
OL,13,Fsubmission that this event would
OL,14,Fpromote campaigns against rights for
OL,15,Fthe transgender community".
OL,17,FIt added that it "takes pride in
OL,18,Fstanding up for those who are
OL,19,Fmarginalised and attacked".
OL,26,@lD@HrrsD@YrrtD@AOUwD@ZO]yD@ROU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,FThe WRN NI said it was "shocked and
OL,8,Fdeeply disappointed" by the decision.
OL,10,FOn Friday, Ruth Paterson from WRN NI
OL,11,Fsaid: "This is all about women's
OL,12,Frights, all about women's bodies, all
OL,13,Fabout women's spaces, all about
OL,14,Fwomen's experiences.
OL,16,F"We absolutely reject any
OL,17,Fcategorisation that we are not
OL,18,Fsupporting the trans community at this
OL,19,Fevent, and trans people are welcome,
OL,20,Fand we're happy to have that
OL,21,Fdiscussion."
OL,26,@lD@HrroD@XOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons MLA
OL,8,Fsaid: "You have to adhere to the
OL,9,Fconditions that are attached to any
OL,10,Fgrant that is given. Public money
OL,11,Fneeds to be accountable. We need to
OL,12,Fhave governance for it as well.
OL,14,F"It shouldn't come as a surprise to
OL,15,Fanybody that there are checks in place
OL,16,Fto make sure that money is being used
OL,17,Fin the right way and that we don't
OL,18,Fhave a breach of law. There are
OL,19,Fsection 75 obligations in play.
OL,26,@lD@Hrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,F"We also have our own rules in
OL,8,Frelation to ensuring that there is a
OL,9,Fquality of opportunity for all of
OL,10,Fthose that are involved. So, this
OL,11,Fisn't about me taking a decision to
OL,12,Fremove any funding. This is about
OL,13,Fensuring that people sign up and obey
OL,14,Fthe rules that they sign up to."
OL,26,@lD@Hrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,FIn response to the minister, Ruth
OL,8,FPaterson said: "I don't think Gordon
OL,9,FLyons is entirely right. I think that
OL,10,Fif you are funded by the public
OL,11,Fsector, you have to follow the public
OL,12,Fsector equality duties and you have to
OL,13,Fhave consideration for everyone."
OL,15,FBoth Feile an Phobail and WRN NI met
OL,16,Fon Friday afternoon.
OL,18,FFollowing the meeting, in a statement
OL,19,FWRN NI said they "appreciate the Feile
OL,20,Fteam taking the time to meet us".
OL,26,@lD@HrrwD@Grr{D@crr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,F"Regrettably, despite engaging in good
OL,8,Ffaith, the meeting did not result in a
OL,9,Fsatisfactory resolution.
OL,11,F"Our concerns have not been addressed,
OL,12,Fand no agreement was reached to
OL,13,Freinstate our event," they added.
OL,15,F"We wrote to Feile to inform them that
OL,16,Fwe would commence legal proceedings if
OL,17,Four event was not reinstated.
OL,26,@lD@HrrwD@Orr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,F"We are now left with no choice but to
OL,8,Fproceed. Our legal proceedings can be
OL,9,Fwithdrawn at any time should Feile
OL,10,Fdecide to reinstate the event."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Feile an Phobail in a
OL,13,Fstatement said they were "extremely
OL,14,Fdisappointed that legal
OL,15,Frepresentatives for the Women's Rights
OL,16,FNetwork filed legal papers with the
OL,17,Fcourt" before the meeting concluded.
OL,26,@lD@HrrqD@_rrtD@Mrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
