PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784922490
OL,3,CWomen's group begin legal process
OL,4,Cafter Feile event cancelled over trans
OL,5,Crights
OL,7,FFeile an Phobail "will continue to
OL,8,Fpromote events which provide balance
OL,9,Fand inclusivity, and encourage those
OL,10,Fwho are marginalised to get involved
OL,11,Fin Feile".
OL,13,F"Feile's decision to withdraw this
OL,14,Fevent stands."
OL,16,FJ K Rowling offered support to WRN NI
OL,17,Fearlier this week.
OL,19,FShe said her foundation "will help
OL,20,Fwith legal costs".
OL,26,@lD@HrroD@BrrsD@ErruD@Crr{D@YOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
