OL,5,Crights
OL,7,FUTV reached out to an organisation
OL,8,Frepresenting the LGBTQ+ community.
OL,10,FThey didn't want to provide a comment
OL,11,Fand said that they were focusing on
OL,12,FBelfast Pride at the weekend.
